text: Djordje Vujicic (; born 15 April 1995) is a Serbian football player who plays for Austrian club FC Tillmitsch. ==Club career== ===Slovenia=== In 2009, he joined academy of football club NK Celje at age 14. He played in Nk Celje for 7 years. He played the Stiker position and left or right Winger. When he was playing for U16 NK Celje he was called in Slovenia national team U16 and later U17. Then he go to Austria. ===Austria=== He played for 4 different clubs. TUS Paldau, FC Ligist, SV Flavia Solva and FC Tillmitsch, in 2 and a half seasons he scored 45 goals in 53 matches.
